{"type": "article", "id": 16475, "title": "Quido 玻璃瓶", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-23T06:40:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 66, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135544lno3hRUCv2JNzaAY.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个玻璃做的饮料瓶，自带两根玻璃吸管，特别适合喝带柠檬片的水。圆球体的外形也自带装饰性，里面泡上玫瑰花瓣，也是一个花瓶。设计师曾经设计了带有一根吸管的饮料瓶 HALM，这个改良版多了一份分享。可容纳 300 毫升，售价 26 欧元。<a href=\"http://jakobsendesign.com/shop/quido-300-ml/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143727wDa7e9KMV0zlHdpI.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"750\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143727T0oEKhiWBYx8nC1r.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"750\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143727aJSAp4EZm03jfIWh.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"750\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}